author: Marcy Gonzalez
text:
Sneak peek of my WIP:
Dangerous. A man who had been tormented through time and people.
He stared down Nanny Olive, face blank, and she balked.
"You are to blame." He said in a flat voice.
And the Nanny sneered.
"For what?" #writing #WritingCommunity

author: Marcy Gonzalez
text:
She was everything, the moon to his sea,
And he made her as happy as could be.
No matter the distance, far or wide.
It was a love so strong that it could never die.
And although the union was brief
It was a moment that brought nothing but peace. #poetrycommunity
